PROJECT RULES

1. Backend is source of truth
2. Never invent API fields
3. Always use real endpoints
4. Always handle loading, empty, error, success states
5. Do not create giant screen files
6. Split logic into small components
7. Keep navigation stable
8. Avoid multiple uncontrolled modals
9. Use consistent date/time formatting
10. Do not redesign the app unless explicitly asked
11. Output complete working code only
12. Preserve existing structure